body:
Hey!

Have you ever had a horrible/embarrassing autocorrect mistake happen? Well, share it down below! This is like avicus quotes in a way, but for funny mistakes that happened. I'll start off.

I was messaging someone one day, and while I was typing I meant to say "Kk", but it autocorrected to say KKK. So the text went like "KKK will see you there". 

I hope lots of you respond!
